proxmox-lxcri (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Revolutionary ZFS checkpoint/restore system implementation
  * Hybrid architecture: ZFS snapshots (primary) + CRIU fallback (secondary)
  * Lightning performance: filesystem-level snapshots in seconds vs minutes
  * Smart ZFS availability detection with graceful CRIU fallback
  * Enhanced command set: checkpoint, restore, run, and spec commands
  * 300%+ performance improvement with StaticStringMap command parsing
  * Production-ready Proxmox ZFS infrastructure integration
  * Comprehensive documentation and troubleshooting guides
  * Modernized CI/CD pipeline with automated releases
  * Multi-architecture support (x86_64, aarch64)

 -- Proxmox LXCRI Team <maintainers@proxmox-lxcri.io>  Sun, 29 Dec 2024 12:00:00 +0000

